    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;<font face="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="14px" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span style="font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; float: none; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; font-variant: normal; font-size: 14px; text-transform: none">The host cache is enabled by default. To disable it, start the server with the</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><a class="link" href="http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.0/en/server-options.html#option_mysqld_skip-host-cache" style="margin-left: 0px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(1, 90, 132); padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-position: initial initial; border: 0px; background-repeat: repeat; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-left: 0px; line-height: 25px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding-right: 0px; text-transform: none; margin-right: 0px"><code class="option" style="margin-left: 0px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(14, 64, 117); padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Courier New, Courier, fixed, monospace; border: 0px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: underline; background-color: white; padding-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 13px; margin-right: 0px"><u><font face="Courier New, Courier, fixed, monospace" size="13px" color="rgb(14, 64, 117)">--skip-host-cache</font></u></code></a><font face="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="14px" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><span style="font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; float: none; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; font-variant: normal; font-size: 14px; text-transform: none">option.</span></font>&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      &#30475;&#26469;mysql&#23448;&#26041;&#26159;&#40664;&#35748;&#21457;&#24067;&#23601;&#25552;&#20379;&#27492;&#20301;&#32622;&#23433;&#20840;&#30340;&#35774;&#32622;&#30340;&#65292;&#24456;&#35880;&#24910;&#21834;!
