    <pre class="bbcodeblock" dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding-left: 3px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant: normal; font-size: 13px; width: 759.5px; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; font-style: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 0px; height: 66px; padding-bottom: 3px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 3px; border: 1px inset; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal; padding-top: 3px; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); margin-right: -99999px">Stopping VirtualBox kernel module                          [  OK  ]
