      &#26597;&#30475;http://www.linuxquestions.org/questions/linux-desktop-74/latest-version-of-virtualbox-kernel-errors-on-centos-5-i386-645991/
    </p>
    <p>
      &#12304;&#21407;&#25991;&#12305;
    </p>
    <font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">Hi. You're in luck because I'm doing the same exact thing (except my server is x86_64.)</font><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">You will need the kernel sources. Downloading kernel-devel or kernel-headers does not work. CentOS kernel sources aren't available through yum, so I used these steps from the CentOS wiki.</font><a target="_blank" style="white-space: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 156); font-variant: normal; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255)" href="http://wiki.centos.org/HowTos/I_need_the_Kernel_Source"><font color="rgb(34, 34, 156)" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">http://wiki.centos.org/HowTos/I_need_the_Kernel_Source</font></a><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><b style="white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant: normal; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255)">Getting CentOS kernel sources to build VirtualBox kernel module</b></font><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">of course, you may not run some of these commands if you already have the packages installed.</font><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /></font><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><i style="white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant: normal; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255)">as root:</i></font><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br align="start" style="background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal" /></font>

    <div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px; background-color: rgb(207, 217, 255); text-transform: none; line-height: normal; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 20px; word-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
      <div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom: 2px; font-size: 11px">
